Description of amendment request: 

The proposed amendment would revise Technical Specification 3.7.1.1 (Tables 3.7-1 and 3.7-2). Tables 2.2-1 and
3.3-2, and Bases 3/4.7. Tables 3.7-1, 3.7-2, 3.3-2, and 2.2-1 would be revised to provide appropriate margin to relax
