GPU Nuclear Corporation, et al., Docket No. 50-219, Oyster Creek Nuclear Generating Station, Ocean County, New Jersey




Date of application for amendment: 

September 26, 1994 


Brief description of amendment: 

The amendment revises the license condition regarding the ``Plan for the Long Range Planning Program.'' The amendment
revises the Plan by changing the semi-annual reporting period to annual, and to reflect refined evaluation criteria
and assessment methodology, and to incorporate necessary changes to the license condition wording.


