Indiana Michigan Power Company, Docket No. 50-316, Donald C. Cook, Nuclear Plant, Unit No. 2, Berrien County, Michigan




Date of application for amendment: 

February 22, 1994


Brief description of amendment: 

The amendment revises the Technical Specifications (TS) for pressure vessel heatup and cooldown curves and extends
the applicability from 12 effective full power years (EFPYs) of operation to 15 EFPYs. The TS changes are based on an
analysis of the Cook Unit 2 surveillance capsule U which was removed after exposure of 8.65 EFPYs.


Date of issuance: 

 November 25, 1994


Effective date: 

November 25, 1994


